{"tid":429950,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[澳洲中部] 在世界中心呼喚。愛六日","createTime":"2017-10-09T11:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T12:42:55.000Z","uid":127522,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"522cc33d1ae57b909ba3f2c89e85c941a9442682","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"[Day 1] 悉尼 (Sydney) &gt; Alice Springs<br />\n<br />\n小編居於悉尼, 是日由悉尼飛往澳洲北領地第二大城市 Alice Springs, 開始感受中澳紅土沙漠風情<br />\n<br />\n航班資料：<br />\nQFA790 (QF790)<br />\nYSSY (SYD) 0935 (UTC+11)// YBAS (ASP) 1125(UTC+9.5)<br />\n表定航程: 03:25<br />\n航機: 波音737-800"},{"pid":"dc692e201f6eb38078cc975b1a06450afe80d276","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/193608_617cc0893e70d772527ad21be4c23f61.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F193608_617cc0893e70d772527ad21be4c23f61.JPG&h=0b152402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAlice Springs Airport<br />\n到達後即市內觀光，前往 Stuart Goal 及 The Residency"},{"pid":"d4812ebf7e6e40a005e17fa5bc6fc242e3e4752d","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"Stuart Gaol 始建於1907年, 為Alice Springs現存最古老的建築物，亦為一所在1938年關閉的監獄, 內有刑具展館<br />\n<br />\n入場費：$2<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/esKcb7Z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FesKcb7Z&h=d9d4625c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa6be3625932a3f81ba9a2f460be0caa6f58955f","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/esKcb7Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FesKcb7Z.jpg&h=46246b19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1462080d27d9160bae0abcd8f02036b1cc16c3d","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"The Residency 則建於1926年，為中澳洲總督居所，由於Alice Springs 夏季可達45-47 度，房屋擁有特厚隔熱磚牆，歷來英國皇室成員訪問時均居於此，包括1963年女皇訪澳"},{"pid":"6eda7186b02c33d95f66160436bed488f736755c","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/22179711_10213828655811768_3143013990266070410_o.jpg?oh=ee62eb71de1a99e03642855bb51eedf5&amp;oe=5A79598D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F22179711_10213828655811768_3143013990266070410_o.jpg%3Foh%3Dee62eb71de1a99e03642855bb51eedf5%26oe%3D5A79598D&h=9140b913&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fd30b7d98d9cf8e229cb33f931b77a36ccf68aa","tid":429950,"uid":148785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"居於墨爾本，想去好耐，<br />\n但想左好耐都冇行動，<br />\n入黎留個名先"},{"pid":"41aec6b91579d9c1db56d15fbdf0d88d1aa0c4b2","tid":429950,"uid":36672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:37:42.000Z","msg":"好多阿寶同烏蠅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b63fc4c0c27bb26cfe75f9f4c17c3ffb5eceb05","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"市內遊畢即前往城鎮中心700米外之Anzac Hill （澳紐軍團山）觀賞日落, 是日日落為18:35, 觀賞澳洲中部原野及Alice Springs/ McDonald Range 全景同時想象澳紐軍團騎兵在一戰東線戰場馳騁的場景，緬懷澳紐軍團在一戰為保衛大英帝國利益在加利波底所作之犠牲<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/090613_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F090613_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f5e91bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/090639_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F090639_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4acdaf21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55a507c7b167ba957742009d99a36c13e38f9f4a","tid":429950,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:22:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"800ff27f4abb514853bb46e0f8027104131116cb","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:32:32.000Z","msg":"Day 1-2 均居於鄰近城鎮中心Todd Mall 之Aurora Hotel <br />\n<br />\nDay 2 Alice Springs &gt; Desert Park &gt; Simpsons Gap (West MacDonald Ranges) &gt; Rainbow Valley<br />\n<br />\n是日由城鎮中心向西行，0600 向Desert Park 出發, 本日天氣預報為晴朗無雲，氣溫為38度，有相當高機會脫水。由於天氣及預定要步行7公里進入荒野，因此攜帶3公升水及急救藥物。<br />\n<br />\n0700 由Alice Springs Post office 搭400 前往Desert Park 觀看澳洲獨有之沙漠及乾旱環境生態（一日只有3-4班，因此必須準時）, 入場費為32澳元（已提早預訂）<br />\n<br />\n公園分為三部分，Desert Rivers, Sand Kingdom 及Woodland, 其中心之夜行生物館禁止攝影"},{"pid":"e25ec623666e2b43913f6effc2915dc4550b3b28","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/104112_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F104112_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7bed4e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/104121_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F104121_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a09f7293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/104135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F104135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=171ab87b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/104145_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F104145_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c6542a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/104154_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F104154_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8f7a3e3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a76477c60e7b5034542ac73b3627d9d33d8e742","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:51:34.000Z","msg":"1300 離開公園徒步4公里前往Simpsons Gap, 欣賞沙漠中的一線天"},{"pid":"e679ca591b99dbd5cd9505fa647fa91ffc882963","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fcbr1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/22256605_10213848182819931_6370784304358194792_o.jpg?oh=38f54bbcfa3cff420b1bc74e5b0d2562&amp;oe=5A728E51\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fcbr1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F22256605_10213848182819931_6370784304358194792_o.jpg%3Foh%3D38f54bbcfa3cff420b1bc74e5b0d2562%26oe%3D5A728E51&h=c3d83696&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1428dd10651b16be084125f3118b033242bfe81","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"1700乘坐的士前往Rainbow Valley, 欣賞沙岩(Sandstone) 地貌，由於沙岩較難風化，因此形成Inselburg（孤山）"},{"pid":"e0c67d6f8ef4af1f0e32ca8723ebde8d2155dad3","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fcbr1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/22256575_10213834892967693_9075418706631766500_o.jpg?oh=690a506a4e6a6649d2eb8fc939f00eef&amp;oe=5A43E390\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fcbr1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F22256575_10213834892967693_9075418706631766500_o.jpg%3Foh%3D690a506a4e6a6649d2eb8fc939f00eef%26oe%3D5A43E390&h=f95668f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14c2c3d41447c797f1b71cc48bad7f42f95a22c0","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:12:53.000Z","msg":"Day 3: Alice Springs &gt; Uluru (Ayers Rock) &gt; 度假村自由購物<br />\n<br />\n是日前往Uluru 度假村，航班資訊:<br />\n<br />\nQJE1941 (QF1941)<br />\nYBAS (ASP) 1335 (UTC+9.5)// YAYE (AYQ) 1420(UTC+9.5)<br />\n表定航程: 0: 45<br />\n航機: Qantas Link波音717-200<br />\n<br />\nAyers Rock Resort 位於Uluru 18公里的Yulara，為免騷擾原住民社區，澳洲政府在80​​年代為旅客建立Yulara前進補給站，以免旅客在原住民社區／國家公園内夜宿。"},{"pid":"6bd5cfcd4fe649189bb310d0e523f17d78da5fd5","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"Day 3 <br />\n<br />\n0500 前往城鎮2公里以北之Telegraph Station, 內含澳洲中部探險史簡介。Alice Springs前稱Stuart, 為始建於1871年澳洲南北橫貫電報線之中間站。Alice Springs為沙漠中之綠洲，因此探險家均在此補給。如上述，遊畢回酒店退房加上前往機場。"},{"pid":"dc4b6d5ca2a26e80f24b9fa217d31ad82d2749dd","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/112029_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F112029_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9592a164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電報站"},{"pid":"9e046c4a0d45f9c93d3e6613684a25f5b9f06e02","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"度假村內有四間旅館，分別為Emu Waking Apartments, Sails in the desert, Ayers Rock Campsite 及Outback Pioneer , 今次住Backpacker 旅館之Outback Pioneer"},{"pid":"fa61c70879c1ec69e194055648dce65d27a5ceb5","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:25:42.000Z","msg":"Ayers Rock Resort <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coxarchitecture.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/281017_00_N2_highresjpg-e1449802336582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coxarchitecture.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F281017_00_N2_highresjpg-e1449802336582.jpg&h=9e23756a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5950ebf1b31c00cea96947246615180a9148bf05","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"Day 4 <br />\n<br />\nUluru- Kata Tjuta National Park (Sunrise Tour &gt; Base and Kuniya Walk &gt; Waterhole &gt; Sunset Tour)<br />\n<br />\n請注意：Uluru 為原住民阿南努人(Anangu)人上三萬五千年之家園及聖地，阿南努人認為此地為祖先神靈居住之地，世代守護族人，有個別地區為部族男/女族人儀式之地，蘊藏族人才懂之秘密，因此嚴禁攝錄，請尊重原住民文化，抱虔敬之心前往此地。<br />\n<br />\n同時，阿南努人極不歡迎旅客攀爬Uluru, 此行為被認為踐踏祖先。而且，攀爬70度途為極度危險之行為同時，嚴禁帶走任何石頭，會帶來厄運。<br />\n<br />\n本日主要為Local Tour, 其中AAT kings 提供免費機場接送及Local tour, 可在旅行社或在度假村預訂。<br />\n<br />\n日出：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/114721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F114721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4a106a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/114734_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F114734_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=158230cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62a4817dd876ea11fdef3510546a051e96f89860","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:04:05.000Z","msg":"國家公園入場費為25澳元，有效期3日<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/120338_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F120338_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7e13a077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原野日落，Day 3"},{"pid":"8729d91394eace0de078e3506a3bc72cae8e54c7","tid":429950,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"154f7067afbacd349c2993fc14840052c7f80f8a","tid":429950,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爬過Ayer rock</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}